<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7635003>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Dudanus pallidus Dlabola (Austria, Hainburg). A–D: aedeagus. A: lateral view; B: ventrolateral view; C: apical view; D: ventral view; E: right genital plate, ventral view; F: left style, dorsal view; G: female pregenital sternite." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7635003/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7635005>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Dudanus javieri Remane & Della Giustina (Spain, Alcañiz).A–D: aedeagus.A: lateral view; B: ventrolateral view; C: apical view; D: ventral view; E: left genital plate, ventral view; F: left style, dorsal view; G: female pregenital sternite." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7635005/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7634997>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Dudanus karra n. sp. (Friuli, Basovizza), aedeagus.A: lateral view; B: ventrolateral view; C: apical view; D ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7634997/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7634999>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Dudanus karra n. sp. (Friuli, Basovizza). A: right genital plate, ventral view; B: left genital plate, dorsal view; C: left style, dorsal view; D: connective, ventral view; E: pygofer and anal tube, lateral (and slightly dorsocaudal) view (bristles of right pygofer lobe displaced, anal tube raised); F: Female pregenital sternite." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7634999/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7634995>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Dudanus karra n. sp. (Slovenia, Rakitovec). A: brachypterous male; B: brachypterous female; C: macropterous female; D: last nymphal instar; E: male, frontal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7634995/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7635001>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Dudanus karra n. sp. (Friuli, Basovizza), female. A: 1st valvula, apical portion; B: 2nd valvula, apical portion." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7635001/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7635009>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Dudanus spp. distribution maps. A: Dudanus javieri Remane & Della Giustina (♦), D. pallidus Dlabola (●), D. karra n. sp. (■); B: Localities of D. karra n. sp. in north-eastern Italy and in Slovenia." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7635009/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7635007>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Localities with Dudanus karra n. sp. A: Valle d’Aosta, Riserva Naturale della Gargantua; B, C: Friuli-Venezia Giulia (Trieste), Basovizza, Monte Stena; D: Slovenia, Rakitovec; E: Slovenia, Socerb; F: Stipa pennata s.l. (photos A:Archivio regionale—Struttura Biodiversità, sostenibilità e aree naturali protette; E, F: M. Skok)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7635007/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

